d the world."}, {"title": "Kaye, Rod ", "site_url": "http://www.rodkaye.com/", "description": "Biography, tearsheets, and galleries including samples of sports and scenic photography with and without Shockwave enhancement. Information on his darkroom technique."}, {"title": "Kennedy, Allison ", "site_url": "http://www.allisonkennedy.com/", "description": "Action photography, including motocross, snowboarding, and snowcross, as well as a selection of images from other assignments."}, {"title": "Kim, Sang-Hoon - Kish ", "site_url": "http://www.kishkim.com/", "description": "Gallery of journalistic and documentary photography. Celebrity shots, landscapes, cityscape, biography and contact details. Bilingual site (Korean and English)."}, {"title": "Kocho-Schellenberg, Alexandra ", "site_url": "http://www.aksphoto.me.uk/", "description": "Photo reportage on topics in Russia, the US, UK, and Turkey."}, {"title": "Koren, Ziv ", "site_url": "http://www.zivkoren.com/", "description": "Israeli Photojournalist, photos of  Israel's conflict with the Palestinians, former Israeli prime minister Ehud Barak, the Pope in the holy land, and covers for Time Magazine."}, {"title": "Kraft, Brooks ", "site_url": "http://www.brookskraft.com/", "description": "Photojournalist's portfolio of people, place and politics - featuring George Bush and bullfighting. Includes contact information and short biography."}, {"title": "Krieger, Herman ", "site_url": "http://members.efn.org/~hkrieger/", "description": "Selections from photo essays shot primarily in the Eugene, Oregon area, including \"Churches ad hoc\", \"Along West 11th Avenue\", and \"A Day in the Life of a Mobile Veterinarian\"."}, {"title": "Ladefoged, Joachim ", "site_url": "http://www.joachimladefoged.com/", "description": "Danish photographer known for his black and white work on Albania. Site also features a story on refugees in Kenya."}, {"title": "Lazar, John ", "site_url": "http://www.johnlazar.com/", "description": "Gallery of 